Rating: 4
I use 1 lb. salted butter a bit cooler than room temperature. 1-2 lb. bag of powdered sugar. 1 tablespoon Mexican vanilla, 1 teaspoon almond. Combine in stand up mixer and slowly add heavy cream to consistency speed up the mixer and whip to fluff up. I like to add a piped border to my cakes so don't overdo the cream. Fantastic on chocolate cake. made his dozens of times, always rave reviews and requests for the recipe.

