I used this to frost a chocolate banana cake. For those with an Asian palate* for sweetness versus American palate, half the sugar. Also be a little more liberal with the salt if you like the contrast between the sweetness and saltiness of the frosting. * Asian palate = generally, Asian desserts are less sweet than American desserts. To suit my and my Asian friends' palates, I notice that I generally have to half the sugar content of the American desserts found on Epicurious.

